age-360459%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETo%20date%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20rejuvenated%2040%20wells%20and%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFast%20forward%20to%202024%2C%20people%20are%20now%20using%20air%20conditioners%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20never%20had%20such%20harsh%20summers%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20up%20as%20his%20responsibility%2C%20Kapil%20started%20%E2%80%98SayTrees%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20creating%20urban%20and%20rural%20forests%2C%20and%20rejuvenating%20lakes%20with%20support%20from%20corporations%20and%20the%20community.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20planted%203.8%20million%20trees%20across%20the%20country%20and%20rejuvenated%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20founder%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20has%20achieved%20this%20feat%20through%20community%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETo%20revive%20Bengaluru%20to%20its%20initial%20glory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20in%20detail%20about%20his%20motivation%20to%20start%20SayTrees%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20roads%20were%20covered%20with%20giant%20trees.%20The%20cover%20was%20so%20dense%20that%20one%20could%20not%20see%20the%20sun.%20One%20day%20when%20I%20was%20travelling%20from%20home%20to%20office%2C%20I%20was%20as%20usual%20looking%20at%20the%20tall%20trees%20on%20the%20roads.%20The%20other%20morning%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20all%20those%20trees%20were%20gone.%20It%20was%20disheartening%20for%20me%20as%20I%20valued%20them%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20trees%20were%20being%20chopped%20down%20for%20road%20widening%20and%20metro%20construction.%20Although%20the%20Government%20was%20transplanting%20them%2C%20I%20felt%20responsible%20as%20a%20citizen.%20Otherwise%2C%20Bengaluru%20would%20become%20like%20any%20other%20Indian%20city.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20regret%20later%20that%20I%20could%20have%20done%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20began%20visiting%20government%20offices%20to%20understand%20his%20role%20and%20capacity%20as%20a%20citizen.%20In%202007%2C%20he%20started%20planting%20saplings%20on%20weekends.%20Every%20year%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20began%20joining%20him%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20SayTrees%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20weekend%20initiative%20has%20now%20grown%20into%20an%20active%20group%20of%20100%20people%20who%20conduct%20afforestation%20drives%20across%20the%20country%20with%20community%20engagement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20it%20was%20important%20that%20people%20come%20and%20join%20this%20movement%20to%20make%20this%20initiative%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20after%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20organisation%20began%20working%20on%20water%20conservation%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20sapling%20needs%20support%20for%20two%20to%20three%20years%2C%20including%20regular%20watering.%20However%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20after%20planting%20saplings%20during%20the%20monsoon%2C%20it%20became%20challenging%20to%20find%20water%20to%20sustain%20them%20in%20the%20summer.%20While%20working%20on%20our%20plantation%20projects%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20water%20conservation%20also%20needs%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERejuvenating%20the%20once%20%E2%80%98City%20of%20Lakes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20aptly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98City%20of%20Lakes%E2%80%99%2C%20Bengaluru%20boasted%20a%20large%20number%20of%20lakes%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20kings%20and%20the%20British.%20Satellite%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20Bangalore%20Metropolitan%20Region%20Development%20Authority%20(BMRDA)%20in%202001%20revealed%20that%20there%20were%202%2C789%20lakes%20in%20the%20city.%20Over%20time%2C%20many%20of%20these%20lake%20areas%20were%20transformed%20into%20residential%20and%20commercial%20entities%2C%20educational%20institutes%2C%20bus%20stands%2C%20stadiums%2C%20and%20dumping%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXeccEy40hIKxFxKprPQQnK8Ne8IwphvqqnbZ0RvhrIknhPZnfU_rLDHUgtIOPKEdhDYIdOxlg6F_JBJu6JSzxS12PatbDpdXUtrNddvTvAaOkELl23Sarsp7KOvvtbtxhCwvbPA3GcACZsE25IoeD51fcQ%3Fkey%3Dbh9p4Y9Cbw8RlZeCoJr9pA%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20lakes%20are%20drying%20up%20owing%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20uncontrolled%20development%20in%20the%20city.%20With%20more%20population%20concentration%2C%20resources%20are%20being%20utilised%20fast%20and%20the%20city%20is%20turning%20into%20a%20concrete%20jungle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20SayTrees%20began%20focusing%20on%20water%20conservation%20in%20addition%20to%20tree%20planting.%20To%20date%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20rejuvenated%2040%20wells%20and%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20credits%20his%20three%20P%E2%80%99s%20formula%20%E2%80%94%20project%2C%20people%2C%20and%20paisa%20(money)%20%E2%80%94%20for%20their%20success%20in%20achieving%20this%20feat.%20%E2%80%9CFinding%20the%20right%20project%2C%20the%20right%20people%2C%20and%20the%20right%20corporate%20partners%20for%20funding%20support%20is%20crucial.%20I%20involve%20communities%20who%20are%20equally%20passionate%20about%20these%20initiatives%20to%20ensure%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20success%20and%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20they%20rejuvenated%20Choodasandra%20lake%2C%20which%20spans%2023%20acres%20in%20the%20city.%20Talking%20about%20its%20before%20and%20after%20conditions%2C%20Kapil%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20lake%20was%20filled%20with%20sewage%20and%20waste.%20It%20took%20us%20a%20year%20to%20clean%20it.%20We%20have%20created%20a%20grazing%20land%2C%20a%20green%20patch%20for%20birds%2C%20and%20a%20walking%20track%20for%20the%20community.%20Now%2C%20both%20people%20and%20biodiversity%20can%20enjoy%20peaceful%20evenings%20near%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20says%20it%20cost%20the%20organisation%20Rs%204%20crore%20to%20complete%20this%20project.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20expensive%20affair%20that%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20through%20corporate%20support.%20We%20make%20sure%20to%20involve%20the%20community%20to%20ensure%20the%20sustainability%20of%20the%20rejuvenation%20efforts.%20The%20community%20acts%20as%20additional%20hands%20and%20eyes%20for%20us%2C%20because%20while%20rejuvenation%20is%20easier%2C%20maintaining%20the%20lake%20is%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20diverted%20some%20of%20the%20incoming%20sewage%20and%20kept%20the%20rest%20to%20ensure%20a%20steady%20flow%20of%20water%20into%20the%20lake.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20created%20sedimentation%20ponds%20and%20wetlands%20that%20filter%20the%20incoming%20water%20before%20it%20reaches%20the%20lake.%20Rains%20are%20only%20seasonal%2C%20so%20maintaining%20a%20consistent%20water%20flow%20is%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kapil%20says%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20with%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKapil%20says%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20recharge%20groundwater%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20steps%20involved%20in%20the%20lake%20rejuvenation%20drives%2C%20he%20explains%20that%20first%2C%20they%20identify%20the%20lakes%20that%20need%20urgent%20rejuvenation.%20Secondly%2C%20they%20prepare%20a%20detailed%20project%20report%20(DPR)%2C%20which%20includes%20information%20on%20the%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20topography%2C%20ecology%2C%20funds%2C%20and%20everything%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20benefit%20the%20community%20and%20biodiversity.%20Thirdly%2C%20they%20obtain%20approval%20from%20the%20government%20authorities.%20Finally%2C%20they%20proceed%20with%20the%20restoration%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kapil%2C%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20with%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20%E2%80%9CA%20large%20lake%20can%20store%20up%20to%20200%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20every%20monsoon.%20Imagine%20gallons%20of%20rainwater%20flowing%20down%20the%20drain%20and%20flooding%20the%20city.%20Lakes%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20capture%20that%20rainwater%2C%20which%20can%20then%20support%20the%20city%20during%20the%20summer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20miles%20away%20from%20India%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20in%20the%20US%20since%202015%2C%20but%20this%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20affected%20the%20organisation%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20only%20grown%20since%20then.%20Although%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20visit%20home%20often%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20my%20parents%20angry!%20%E2%80%94%20I%20ensure%20to%20return%20to%20India%20once%20every%20year%20to%20monitor%20the%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20cannot%20do%20this%20work%20alone.%20Bengaluru%20alone%20has%20200%20lakes.%20If%20we%20rejuvenate%2010%20each%20year%2C%20it%20will%20take%20us%2020%20more%20years.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%20have%20that%20much%20time.%20People%20can%20join%20hands%20with%20us%20so%20that%20together%20we%20can%20rejuvenate%20more%20and%20more%20lakes%20and%20be%20responsible%20citizens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVolunteer%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saytrees.org%2Fvolunteer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESayTrees%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20and%20build%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20all.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita