rgy%20for%20industrial%20operations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Merino%20Industries%20has%20been%20an%20early%20adopter%20of%20solar%20energy%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20exploring%20renewable%20energy%20options%20from%20wind%20plants.%20The%20impact%20is%20notable.%20In%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-24%2C%20only%2018.2%20percent%20of%20their%20energy%20needs%20were%20met%20with%20fossil%20fuels%2C%207.2%20percent%20from%20State%20Electricity%20Boards%20(SEB)%20grids%2C%20and%20massive%2074.6%20percent%20from%20renewable%20sources.%20By%202027%2C%20they%20aim%20to%20exceed%2090%20percent%20from%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20touched%20a%20milestone%20in%20the%202022-23%20period%2C%20ensuring%20that%20100%20percent%20of%20the%20heat%20energy%20required%20(12.64%20Lakh%20GJ)%20at%20the%20Rohad%20and%20Hapur%20factories%20was%20produced%20in-house%20using%20boilers%20and%20secondary%20furnaces%2C%20primarily%20from%20non-fossil%20fuels%20namely%20rice%20husk%20and%20saw%20dust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncrease%20energy%20efficiency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20Industries%20is%20committed%20to%20achieving%20energy%20efficiency%20in%20every%20operation.%20Less%20energy%20consumption%20should%20yield%20more%20output.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20constantly%20upgrade%20electrical%20tools%2C%20appliances%2C%20and%20machinery%2C%20and%20bring%20in%20improved%20technology%20for%20operations%2C%20utilities%2C%20and%20lighting%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConservation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergy%20consciousness%20extends%20beyond%20factories%20to%20every%20office%20at%20Merino%20Industries.%20Procuring%20and%20using%20energy-saving%20equipment%2C%20machines%2C%20and%20tools%20is%20key%20to%20conserving%20energy%20from%20the%20start.%20Natural%20light%20is%20promoted%2C%20and%20automatic%20lighting%20systems%20reduce%20manual%20int