ndustry%20level.%20However%2C%20Merino%20Industries%E2%80%99%20achievements%20are%20significant.%20Mr%20Lohia%20believes%20this%20could%20serve%20as%20an%20example%20for%20industrial%20establishments%20worldwide.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20massive%20task%20to%20change%20processes%20and%20mindsets.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20succeeded%20by%20doing%20everything%20indigenously%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20points%20out%20that%20strategic%20investment%20decisions%2C%20such%20as%20investing%20in%20automation%20tools%20and%20equipment%2C%20have%20long-term%20payoffs.%20A%20culture%20of%20energy%20consciousness%2C%20from%20top%20management%20to%20the%20bottom%2C%20is%20crucial.%20Simple%20actions%2C%20like%20switching%20off%20unnecessary%20lights%20or%20air%20conditioners%2C%20are%20encouraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommercially%2C%20wealth%20must%20be%20created%20for%20stakeholders.%20At%20Merino%20Industries%2C%20this%20is%20done%20sustainably%2C%20maximising%20the%20circular%20economy%20concept%2C%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%20These%20principles%20are%20championed%20across%20their%2022%20establishments%2C%20five%20factories%2C%20and%2018%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ponds%20at%20the%20Rohad%20factory%20premises%20are%20a%20sustainable%20addition%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-