%2Fparis-2024%2Finterviews%2Fjyothi-yarraji-paris-olympics-100m-hurdles-first-indian-no-pressure-coach-mentor-ramesh-sports-authority-of-india-athletics%2Farticle68362827.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJyothi%20Yarraji%20won%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20pressure%20at%20maiden%20Olympics%20in%20Paris%3A%20Mentor%20and%20coach%20Ramesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3A%20by%20Sportstar%2C%20Published%20on%203%20July%2C%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723108447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360279%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Multiple%20setbacks%2C%20strokes%20of%20bad%20luck%2C%20and%20a%20humble%20upbringing%20didn't%20deter%20Jyothi%20Yarraji%20from%20setting%20and%20breaking%20records.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20her%20nine-year-long%20race%20to%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20where%20she%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20100m%20hurdles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A247%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360279%2Fjyothi-yarraji-paris-olympics-2024-100m-hurdle-first-indian-woman-repechage-event-national-record%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Designed%20Like%20Royal%20Maratha%20Camps%2C%20This%20Heritage%20Stay%20in%20Pune%20is%20Surrounded%20by%201000%20Trees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20stand%20upon%20the%20territory%20that%20marks%20out%20the%2017th%20century-inspired%20Chavni%20resort%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Pune%20(and%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20piece%2C%20it%20is%20sure%20to%20make%20it%20to%20your%20wishlist!)%2C%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20shut%20your%20eyes%20for%20a%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20no%20longer%20a%2021st-century%20being.%20You%20are%20now%20standing%20at%20the%20foothills%20of%20two%20of%20history%E2%80%99s%20best%20works%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Lohagad%20and%20Visapur%20forts%2C%20their%20domes%20melting%20into%20th