laces%20where%20culture%20is%20fading%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20backed%20by%20an%20intent%20to%20get%20native%20and%20non-native%20Maharashtra%20dwellers%20to%20%E2%80%9Cknow%E2%80%9D%20the%20true%20history%20of%20their%20land%2C%20the%20four%20decided%20to%20dive%20into%20a%20project%20that%20would%20render%20this%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20when%20Karlekar%20opens%20a%20letter%20from%20a%20guest%20who%20expresses%20their%20happiness%20at%20having%20chosen%20a%20vacation%20spot%20where%20their%20child%20could%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20history%2C%20she%20smiles.%20Chavni%20has%20achieved%20what%20it%20set%20out%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-1722509927.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chavni%20in%20Pune%20is%20a%20heritage%20resort%20built%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20the%2017-century%20Maratha%20rule%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-1722509927.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-1722509927-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-1722509927-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-1722509927-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-1722509927-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359319%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChavni%20in%20Pune%20is%20a%20heritage%20resort%20built%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20the%2017th-century%20Maratha%20rule%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Karlekar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure